- `platform.go` -- `All()` is not changed per requirements
- No other existing files are touched

### Critical Files for Implementation

- `/home/ketan/project/kapow/.claude/worktrees/worktree/commonapp/tools/kapow/internal/platform/platform.go` - Defines the `Extractor` and `Browser` interfaces that `commonapp.go` must implement
- `/home/ketan/project/kapow/.claude/worktrees/worktree/commonapp/tools/kapow/internal/scraper/browser.go` - Real Browser implementation; critical to understand the tab-isolation behavior (each method creates a new tab)
- `/home/ketan/project/kapow/.claude/worktrees/worktree/commonapp/tools/kapow/internal/platform/platform_test.go` - Existing test patterns to follow for consistency
- `/home/ketan/project/kapow/docs/plans/kapow-j2l-application-platform-scrapers.md` - Parent plan with architecture and data flow context
- `/home/ketan/project/kapow/.claude/worktrees/worktree/commonapp/tools/kapow/internal/scraper/cache.go` - Cache integration pattern the extractor results will flow into
